rchbishop of Canterbury to establish peace between King John and a group of rebel barons. The Magna Carta was completed in 1215 and is now considered to be one of the greatest constitutional documents of all time.","url":"https://www.nationalarchives.gov.uk/education/medieval/magna-carta/","urlTitle":"National Archives - Magna Carta","jurisdictionLevel":1},{"id":1705188,"age":76,"year":"1224","julianDay":2168117,"title":"France Declares War on England","description":"France declared war on England as Louis VIII of France attacked Poitou and northern Gascony.","jurisdictionLevel":1}],"lifeSummary":"When Henry Delaval was born about 1148, in Seaton Delaval, Northumberland, England, United Kingdom, his father, Roger Delaval, was 27 and his mother, Mrs. Roger Delaval, was 27. He married Mrs. Delaval before 1169, in Northumberland, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died in 1226, in Northumberland, England, at the age of 79."},"et":{"Abt 1148–1226":"umbes 1148–1226","1148–1226":"1148–1226","1150–Female":"1150–Surnud","1169–1194":"1169–1194","1123–1181":"1123–1181","1123–Female":"1123–Surnud","before 1169":"enne 1169","before 1148":"enne 1148","Abt 1148":"umbes 1148","1194":"1194","1150":"1150","1181":"1181","1226":"1226","1215":"1215","1148":"1148","1169":"1169","1224":"1224","1123":"1123","Abt 1181":"umbes 1181","Seaton Delaval, Northumberland, England":"Seaton Delaval, Northumberland, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Worcester, Worcestershire, England":"Worcester, Worcestershire, England","Northumberland, England":"Northumberland, England","Northumberland, England, United Kingdom":"Northumberland, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1148–1226":"noin 1148–1226","1148–1226":"1148–1226","1150–Female":"1150–Kuollut","1169–1194":"1169–1194","1123–1181":"1123–1181","1123–Female":"1123–Kuollut","before 1169":"ennen vuotta 1169","before 1148":"ennen vuotta 1148","Abt 1148":"noin 1148","1194":"1194","1150":"1150","1181":"1181","1226":"1226","1215